{"tid":1569720,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"九月中啦，和理非定勇武？","createTime":"2019-09-14T17:12:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T03:18:21.000Z","uid":151822,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8eb3d6b4ed394d12ec564a97cdee93ffef359cea","tid":1569720,"uid":151822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T17:12:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">和理非既角色</span></ins></strong></span><br />\n而家有好多批評和理非既聲音，但請大家記得和理非亦有佢地好重要既作用<br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: brown;\">廣傳新聞消息</span></ins>： fb, ig, twitter 確保香港人唔會善忘<br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: brown;\">國際聯署/ 登廣告</span></ins>： 影響全世界對中共、香港局勢既睇法<br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: brown;\">連儂牆/ 唱歌仔/ 拖手仔</span></ins>： 唔反對，有宣傳作用，但首要將自己人身安全擺第一<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">點解要勇武？</span></ins></strong></span><br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: brown;\">經濟金融先係唯一春袋</span></ins>： 無論係中共、港府定藍絲最擔心既都係香港既經濟，只有「焦土」先可以真正令佢地肉痛<br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: brown;\">拯救義士</span></ins>： 如果行動冷卻，被捕義士入罪既機會只會更高，唯有令抗爭者成為大多數，先會有轉機<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">勇武行動注意事項</span></ins></strong></span><br />\n和理非加埋勇武絕對係香港既主流，如果每次都充分保護對方，不割蔗，一定係我地最大強項。<br />\n而我地最大既弱項就係交通，無論出門定番屋企，而家都係欠缺安全又有效率既交通工具，所以必須盡快解決呢個問題。<br />\n絕對反大台，但討論一定會令行動進步，所以一定要有組織有共識有計劃。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一句講曬，咪分裂。</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"bd9e55f2b44dd2d42b986a02592356fa273dab63","tid":1569720,"uid":135067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T17:12:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915 12點英領 2點半銅鑼灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 